[
    {
        "text": "Hello! Welcome to Michael's Better Business English.",
        "startTime": 1056,
        "endTime": 4057,
        "slowStartTime": 1796,
        "slowEndTime": 6300
    },
    {
        "text": "This month, we're looking at how to make polite requests.",
        "startTime": 4596,
        "endTime": 7993,
        "slowStartTime": 7086,
        "slowEndTime": 12311
    },
    {
        "text": "Here, there are two key areas: culture and language.",
        "startTime": 8490,
        "endTime": 12107,
        "slowStartTime": 12940,
        "slowEndTime": 18503
    },
    {
        "text": "First, culture.",
        "startTime": 12745,
        "endTime": 13799,
        "slowStartTime": 19257,
        "slowEndTime": 21006
    },
    {
        "text": "Often, Japanese business people prefer this indirect style;...",
        "startTime": 14655,
        "endTime": 18458,
        "slowStartTime": 22100,
        "slowEndTime": 27919
    },
    {
        "text": "...giving hints, rather than speaking directly.",
        "startTime": 18907,
        "endTime": 21603,
        "slowStartTime": 28504,
        "slowEndTime": 32613
    },
    {
        "text": "However, be careful.",
        "startTime": 22347,
        "endTime": 23703,
        "slowStartTime": 33499,
        "slowEndTime": 35813
    },
    {
        "text": "In western business culture, we prefer to make direct requests;...",
        "startTime": 24153,
        "endTime": 28900,
        "slowStartTime": 36379,
        "slowEndTime": 43603
    },
    {
        "text": "...clear and easy to understand.",
        "startTime": 29196,
        "endTime": 31054,
        "slowStartTime": 43990,
        "slowEndTime": 46812
    },
    {
        "text": "Of course though, you must use polite English.",
        "startTime": 32095,
        "endTime": 34951,
        "slowStartTime": 48299,
        "slowEndTime": 52703
    },
    {
        "text": "Here, there are three levels of polite English for requesting.",
        "startTime": 35708,
        "endTime": 38905,
        "slowStartTime": 53693,
        "slowEndTime": 58629
    },
    {
        "text": "First one, respectful.",
        "startTime": 40000,
        "endTime": 41458,
        "slowStartTime": 60137,
        "slowEndTime": 62401
    },
    {
        "text": "Respectful is for clients, customers or senior members of your company.",
        "startTime": 42255,
        "endTime": 46646,
        "slowStartTime": 63584,
        "slowEndTime": 70181
    },
    {
        "text": "Here, we often use expressions like, \"Would you,\" or \"May I do something?\"",
        "startTime": 47602,
        "endTime": 52106,
        "slowStartTime": 71579,
        "slowEndTime": 78402
    },
    {
        "text": "Second level, businesslike.",
        "startTime": 53646,
        "endTime": 55598,
        "slowStartTime": 80617,
        "slowEndTime": 83670
    },
    {
        "text": "This is more commonly used with co-workers or people you often work with.",
        "startTime": 56301,
        "endTime": 60705,
        "slowStartTime": 84607,
        "slowEndTime": 91317
    },
    {
        "text": "Here, we often use expressions like, \"Could you,\" or \"Can you?\"",
        "startTime": 61455,
        "endTime": 64952,
        "slowStartTime": 92338,
        "slowEndTime": 97692
    },
    {
        "text": "For example, \"Could you reschedule the meeting to the 10th?\"",
        "startTime": 65644,
        "endTime": 68953,
        "slowStartTime": 98687,
        "slowEndTime": 103652
    },
    {
        "text": "Finally, the last level, casual.",
        "startTime": 70756,
        "endTime": 72951,
        "slowStartTime": 106239,
        "slowEndTime": 109694
    },
    {
        "text": "This should be used with close friends and family.",
        "startTime": 73897,
        "endTime": 76453,
        "slowStartTime": 110988,
        "slowEndTime": 114901
    },
    {
        "text": "Here, we often use expressions like, \"Will you?\"",
        "startTime": 77295,
        "endTime": 79296,
        "slowStartTime": 116110,
        "slowEndTime": 119198
    },
    {
        "text": "For example, \"Will you close the door?\"",
        "startTime": 80049,
        "endTime": 82293,
        "slowStartTime": 120287,
        "slowEndTime": 123667
    },
    {
        "text": "Do be careful with this expression though.",
        "startTime": 83448,
        "endTime": 85356,
        "slowStartTime": 125395,
        "slowEndTime": 128302
    },
    {
        "text": "This can sound a little bit angry...",
        "startTime": 86691,
        "endTime": 89391,
        "slowStartTime": 130255,
        "slowEndTime": 134360
    },
    {
        "text": "...with the feeling, \"Why haven't you done this earlier?\"",
        "startTime": 89954,
        "endTime": 92595,
        "slowStartTime": 135157,
        "slowEndTime": 139190
    },
    {
        "text": "For example, \"Will you send me the report?\"...",
        "startTime": 93350,
        "endTime": 95856,
        "slowStartTime": 140185,
        "slowEndTime": 144057
    },
    {
        "text": "...might feel like \"Why haven't you sent me the report already?\"",
        "startTime": 96198,
        "endTime": 99607,
        "slowStartTime": 144486,
        "slowEndTime": 149689
    },
    {
        "text": "So, only use this with close friends and family.",
        "startTime": 100351,
        "endTime": 102600,
        "slowStartTime": 150705,
        "slowEndTime": 154145
    },
    {
        "text": "So, use this advice to make polite requests.",
        "startTime": 103653,
        "endTime": 107294,
        "slowStartTime": 155685,
        "slowEndTime": 161291
    },
    {
        "text": "Thank you and good luck!",
        "startTime": 107954,
        "endTime": 109199,
        "slowStartTime": 162092,
        "slowEndTime": 164094
    }
]